name: Collapsing Space
description:
Infinite  Runner meets Typing Game. Type fast or perish!
Collect the fuel rods and avoid the asteroids.
Switch Lanes by typing the word at the top of the lane

uses Music from the Album "Osaka Lights" by Timecrawler82:
https://freemusicarchive.org/music/Timecrawler_82/Osaka_Lights/
